@startuml ui-layering-node-tree
!theme plain
skinparam backgroundColor white
skinparam defaultFontName Arial

title UI Layering and Overlay Isolation (Menu Scene)

package "Main Scene Tree" {
  node "Control (root)" as Root
  node "Background" as Bg
  node "MainScreenLogo" as Logo
  node "MainMenuButtons" as Buttons
  node "CanvasLayer" as Layer
  node "VarTreeMainMenu (debug tree)" as VarTree
}

Root --> Bg
Root --> Logo
Root --> Buttons
Root --> Layer
Layer --> VarTree

note right of Buttons
Primary interactive gameplay/menu controls.
Subject to normal UI layout flow.
end note

note right of Layer
Overlay plane separated from main UI flow.
Useful for diagnostics/debug display without
disturbing gameplay-space transform logic.
end note

legend right
|= Node |= Role |
| Control | Scene root and layout owner |
| MainMenuButtons | Main interaction controls |
| CanvasLayer | Overlay boundary |
| VarTreeMainMenu | Runtime variable inspection UI |
endlegend

@enduml

